    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/e5bc7/writing.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"How To Write In English Language\"\n        title=\"How To Write In English Language\"\n        src=\"/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/4b190/writing.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/e07e9/writing.jpg 200w,\n/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/066f9/writing.jpg 400w,\n/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/4b190/writing.jpg 800w,\n/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/e5166/writing.jpg 1200w,\n/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/b17f8/writing.jpg 1600w,\n/static/1bd6d7c4df62d04683b9f0fa674b6568/e5bc7/writing.jpg 5184w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This month I'm building this website for my portfolio and my blog. However, I do not decide wherever will use Bahasa or use the English language.</p>\n<p>But after long reflection, I decided to write all of my blog posts using the English language because I'm also want to learn how to properly write a post or article in English.</p>\n<p>So the step I used to write a post in English is</p>\n<h2>1. Decide what topic I will write</h2>\n<p>The first step is deciding what topic I'm gonna write about for example I want to write about programming like javascript then I will research first the javascript language, what it is, and how to use it.</p>\n<h2>2. Write it</h2>\n<p>After I researched the topic, I will write it into a summary then list it into a list of sub-topic, for now, I mainly write it on my phone using the app for writing markdown GitJournal.</p>\n<h2>3. Check the grammars</h2>\n<p>Lastly, I check the grammars using the Grammarly app, this tool is useful because can instantly check our mistake of the post I already write.</p>\n<p>That's it for now,\r\nHopefully, it also helps you if you want to start writing blog posts in English.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"2021-20-10","title":"Try To Learn How To Write In English Language"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"9b932cc3-59ae-5137-8cbe-f1b173478b44","frontmatter__slug":"/blog/try-write-in-english","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"blog"}}},
